7792:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIMx to select the TIM peripheral
7793:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIM_ExtTRGPrescaler The external Trigger Prescaler.
7794:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7795:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7796:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
7797:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV4: ETRP frequency divided by 4.
7798:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV8: ETRP frequency divided by 8.
