7801:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_INVERTED: active low or falling edge active.
7802:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_NONINVERTED: active high or rising edge active.
7803:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  ExtTRGFilter External Trigger Filter.
7804:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F
7805:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
7806:Drivers/STM32F7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f7xx_hal_tim.c ****   */
